| Detection method | **File or folder exists** |
| Associated with a 32-bit app on 64-bit clients | **No** |

Click **OK**

**Tab 5 — Dependencies:**  
None required — skip.

**Tab 6 — Supersedence:**  
None required — skip.

**Tab 7 — Assignments:**

